          "date": "2011-10-19 08:01:11.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "ORNL-28: Solve reconnecting race between IR and SR",
        "message": "ORNL-28: Solve reconnecting race between IR and SR\n\nif there is a connecting request on the fly when client import is\nnotified by IR, it will set the corresponding conn uuid to a higher\nprio and set imp_force_verify so that it will do reconnection\nimmediately in case RPC timeout happens.\n\nChange-Id: I77e799e1f12b49f3c0271585c1ce812d16dc1ef6\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jay@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
